&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OXFORD UNIVERSITY HOSPITALS Foundation NHS TRUST LOCUM CONSULTANT IN PAEDIATRIC ANAESTHESIA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited to apply for the above post for the Department of Anaesthetics at the John Radcliffe Hospital, Headley Way, Headington, Oxford OX3 9DU.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is required to join the paediatric anaesthetic group at the Oxford University Hospitals Foundation NHS Trust. The Paediatric Anaesthetic Group provides flexible team-working to providing children’s anaesthesia in Oxford. This post has been designed for a candidate with an interest in anaesthesia for paediatric orthopaedic surgery and paediatric general surgery including neonatal surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
